PrecisAppointment of two TEMPORARY ADMINISTRATORS of the Government of NEWFOUNDLAND for the following periods: - the Hon. JOHN O'NEILL April 22 to April 24, 1996 - the Hon. JOHN W. MAHONEY April 25 to May 8, 1996 . and appointment of Hon. JAMES R. GUSHUE as ADMINISTRATOR, effective May 9, 1996, to execute the office and functions of the Lieutenant Governor of Newfoundfland during the absence, illness or other inability of the Lieutenant Governor. .
